1.yum install yum-plugin-versionlock 安装yum版本锁定插件
The /etc/yum/pluginconf.d/versionlock.list will be created on the system.

2.yum versionlock gcc-* 锁定gcc
To install or lock the version of the gcc package, 
add that package name to the /etc/yum/pluginconf.d/versionlock.list file by running:

Yum will attempt to update all packages, while excluding the packages listed in the versionlock file.

3.yum versionlock list 查看版本锁定列表

4.yum versionlock clear 清除列表

